title: Skype Me! - From Single User to Small Enterprise and Beyond.pdf
description:
Bill Campbell, Skype Me! From Single User to Small Enterprise and Beyond 
ISBN: 1597490326 | edition 2005 | PDF | 449 pages | 14 mb

This book is divided into four parts. Part I begins with several chapters on the basics of Skype. Here the reader learns how to install and configure Skype on several platforms including Windows, Max OSX, Linux, and PocketPC. The reader will also learn how to begin making voice over IP calls immediately...
